Params: {2: 'Channel Noise', 3: '(She is an anomaly. Even within the boundaries of knowledge, her birth was special.)'}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: '(She is the enemy of human will, but at the same time, she seems more human than humanity itself.)'}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: '(Unpredictability will throw the world into chaos once more.)'}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: "(No, this isn't what I want. What I want is to control all the variables and prevent falsification, not useless trial and error.)"}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: '(But sometimes, mistakes are a necessity.)'}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: "(I can't understand results that are not grounded in logic and deduction.)"}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: "(Aren't you planning on doing something then?)"}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: '(We have never been chess players, nor are we merely pawns on the chessboard.)'}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: '(Well, then... In this metaphor, what are we?)'}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: '(We are just spectators... We are not qualified to intervene. All we need to do is watch quietly until the chess game is decided.)'}

{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: '(You and I are not qualified, unlike "that person." One day, they will meet. Their destiny—I don\'t know of a more suitable word—will be entangled. Perhaps, the only result will be mutual destruction.)'}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: "(If that's the case, then that is in fact destiny.)"}
{2: 'Channel Noise', 3: "(Looks like you've learnt something, after all... May we speak again at another time.)"}
